{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950680/extras/Steam_wishlist_us.gif?t=1737819573\" /><br>ORIKA is a fun 3D action-adventure and story-rich game inspired from 3D  Platformer games, where the robot ORIKA sets out to clean up polluted water environments. <br>Explore beautiful landscapes, solve puzzles, and overcome challenges in this exciting adventure to restore clean water. Join ORIKA on this thrilling journey to make the world a better place!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950680/extras/cleanEffect-600.gif?t=1737819573\" /><br>Explore beautiful landscapes, solve puzzles, and overcome challenges in this exciting adventure to restore clean water. Join ORIKA on this thrilling journey to make the world a better place!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950680/extras/Collecting600.gif?t=1737819573\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950680/extras/Obstacle1-600.gif?t=1737819573\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950680/extras/CleanObstacle600.gif?t=1737819573\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story Of ORIKA</h2>Awakening at the bottom of a polluted lake near a ruined factory, ORIKA, a small robot with a lost memory except for its name, emerges from the water to receive signals from a nearby boat. Through the radio, a former factory worker, now imprisoned for sabotaging the polluting facility as he told ORIKA, pleads for ORIKA's help. He urges ORIKA to use the boat to clean up the water and sell the waste to upgrade the vessel. In return, he promises assistance in restoring ORIKA's memories. Join ORIKA on this quest to cleanse the environment, enhance the boat, and unravel the mystery of its forgotten past!","background":"https://shared